+
+- targeted compilation;
+- domain functional tests;
+- GitHub CLI adapter tests with mocked subprocess transport;
+- rule tests;
+- `git apply --check`;
+- Graphviz DOT parse;
+- JSON metadata validation;
+- archive integrity and binary/bytecode exclusion.
+
